# CVE-2026-33671: picomatch ReDoS via extglob patterns
# False positive — actual installed version is 4.0.4 (patched).
# pnpm.overrides forces picomatch>=4.0.4 in both package.json files.
# pnpm audit confirms no vulnerable version is installed.
# Trivy misidentifies chokidar@4.0.3 as picomatch@4.0.3 when parsing
# the pnpm lockfile.
CVE-2026-33671
